information.transcription:
Brown & Bigelow, Inc. St. Paul
Specializing in promotional products and calendars
Founded in 1896 by Herbert W. Brown and Henry H. Bigelow

Major supplier of advertising calendars and promotional items
Known for their innovative designs and quality products

Expanded operations to include printing and manufacturing
Acquired several smaller companies to increase market share
